  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1312\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-09 at 16 06 16\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/25482501/8d3f2101-c521-4ce3-8479-b9d641b20fdd\">\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nI tried to quick-fix this, but there's a problem here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/43c7258328a0df542318872624d73899a049ddff/ui/StatusQ/src/StatusQ/Components/StatusDraggableListItem.qml#L124-L130\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/43c7258328a0df542318872624d73899a049ddff/ui/StatusQ/src/StatusQ/Components/StatusDraggableListItem.qml#L304-L308\r\n\r\nThis could be fixed settings `Layout.fillWidth: true` to actions, like usage docs says\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/43c7258328a0df542318872624d73899a049ddff/ui/StatusQ/src/StatusQ/Components/StatusDraggableListItem.qml#L77\r\n, but such QML doesn't load at all.\r\n\r\nAs I understand, you can't reparent to a Layout.\r\n\r\nNOTE: Can be simply tested with Storybook with `StatusChatListAndCategoriesPage.qml` page.",
